402
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:24,900
Xiu'er...?  Xiu'er...

403
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:28,000
Jak si mě to nazvala?

404
00:30:31,420 --> 00:30:34,550
Asi začínám bláznit.

405
00:30:36,660 --> 00:30:38,680
Chuyu...

406
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:42,460
Pojď sem.

407
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:46,880
Pojď...

408
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:49,030
